%N A394404 Decimal expansion of the generalized continued fraction 1 + sqrt(2)/(2 + sqrt(3)/(3 + sqrt(4)/(4 + sqrt(5)/(5 + ...)))).
%H A394404 Paul D. Hanna, <a href="/A394404/b394404.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000</a>
%F A394404 Equals 1 + sqrt(2)/(2 + sqrt(3)/(3 + sqrt(4)/(4 + sqrt(5)/(5 + ...)))).
%F A394404 Also equals 1 + 1/(2*sqrt(1/2) + 1/(3*sqrt(2/(1*3)) + 1/(4*sqrt(1*3/(2*4)) + 1/(5*sqrt(2*4/(1*3*5)) + 1/(6*sqrt(1*3*5/(2*4*6)) + 1/(7*sqrt(2*4*6/(1*3*5*7)) + 1/(8*sqrt(1*3*5*7/(2*4*6*8)) + ... + 1/(2*n*sqrt(A000984(n)/4^n) + 1/((2*n+1)*sqrt(4^n/A002457(n)) + ...))))))))), a continued fraction where A000984(n) = (2*n)!/(n!)^2 and A002457(n) = (2*n+1)!/(n!)^2. - _Paul D. Hanna_, May 11 2026
%e A394404 1.56532117325331957549980714983926316...
